description:
Join Gilt’s 8 million members to get instant access to today's top designers at insider prices. Shop today's best fashions for women, men, kids, and home all at up to 60% off—plus great deals in your city!  

The Gilt app provides free, easy access to:
• Luxury Brands at up to 60% Off: Valentino, John Varvatos, kate spade new york & more!
• New Items Added Daily: Most sales last just 36 hours.
• Sales Start at Noon ET: Bonus sales begin at 9pm ET Sun. and Wed.
• Gilt City: Local offers in New York, Los Angeles, Chicago, San Francisco, Seattle, Boston, Atlanta, Houston, Dallas, Miami, Philadelphia, and Washington DC.
• Real-Time Reminders: Get notified as soon as sales start, waitlist items become available & more. 
• Mobile-Exclusive Sales: Because half the thrill is being first. 

We’d love to hear from you:
• If you’re  a fan of Gilt, please take a moment to rate and review our app.  Help us to get the word out!
• Email us at ipad-feedback@gilt.com.

releaseNotes:
The Gilt app has been updated for all your Holiday shopping needs!  

New in this version:
• Fixes crash-on-launch for users who have saved Facebook login credentials
• Fixes another issue preventing some users from logging in with Facebook accounts

New in version 4.4:
• Gift Finder: Tap on Gifts in the top nav to discover the perfect gifts for everyone on your list.
• Improved In-App Messaging: Stay on top of available discounts and free shipping available to you.
• Quicker start-up: Faster loading equals faster shopping.

And, don’t forget these recent improvements:
• iCloud Keychain: Sign in with one tap.
• Improved Fit Notes: Always find the right size.

If you love Gilt please take a moment to rate our app!
